{"about_the_game":"Tournament Tower is a deckbuilding roguelike game where card battles meet rock-paper-scissors. <br><br>Take part in a never-ending wacky martial arts tournament, set in a world inspired by classic shonen and fighting games, animated frame by frame with a 2010s stylized approach and a bit of western influences.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/steam_title01__2_.png?t=1697796206\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/clash_gif.gif?t=1697796206\" /><br><br>Each card represents a move that belongs to one of three types: Rock, Paper and Scissors. Your move and your opponent\u2019s move are always played at the same time, and the outcome of the round determines both damage dealt and card effects.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/gif-steam__1_.gif?t=1697796206\" /><br><br><br>Face a varied cast of enemies, each one with a different set of moves and behavioral patterns: pay attention to their hints and try to form a strategy, while constantly balancing out risk and reward.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/steam_title02__2_.png?t=1697796206\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/reward_gif.gif?t=1697796206\" /><br><br><br>Add new moves to your deck between each battle, remove the ones you don\u2019t want, while also getting stronger yourself with stat upgrades and passive times.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350260/extras/map_gif.gif?t=1697796206\" /><br><br><br>Each time you get defeated you will have to start a new run, but all of the knowledge you 